<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="Ptyonoprogne_rupestris#Beschreibung"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Beschreibung</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="Ptyonoprogne_rupestris#Lebensraum"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Lebensraum</span></a></li>
